<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Verification Code</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .container { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; }
        .otp-code { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; color: #007bff; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Your Verification Code</h2>
        <p>Use the following OTP to complete your <%= type %>:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        
        <p>This code will expire in <strong><%= expiresIn %></strong>.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Security Tip:</strong> Never share this code with anyone. Our team will never ask for your verification code.</p>
        
        <p>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= year %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>